### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get a single contact
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/6a514efbae1608e99da39f81

### Create a contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "jdoe@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "blue",
  "birthday": "1990-01-01"
}

### Update a contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/64b9d2e1c9f0a1234567890a
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "green",
  "birthday": "1990-01-01"
}

### Delete a contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/64b9d2e1c9f0a1234567890a

